author: edwingo
msg: Added doPrivileged calls to allow code to run in environments such as EJB
and servlet containers which have SecurityManager-s installed.  Note this
new code depends on Java2 and is therefore currently checked into a
separate branch called "java2-branch".  Other changes:
+ Fixed 4989 NPE in TransformerFactory.newInstance() when jaxp.properties
+ Added runtime debug support if system prop "jaxp.debug" is set
This commit was manufactured by cvs2svn to create branch 'java2-branch'.

author: edwingo
msg: Added a "debug" compile option to enable the possibility that the stack
trace shows line numbers.  However, the default value is set to the ant
default of "off" so no debug info is provided, as before.  This is to
maintain backward compatibility.  I think the default should be "on",
instead, though.  I will let someone else change it.
